{
  "texts": [
    "An overview of IoA encompassing heterogeneous autonomous agents across diverse domains, with an illustrative example of cross-domain agent interactions.",
    "Consider two agents operating in distinct domains, e.g., domains 1 and 4.",
    "Initially, each agent registers with a proxy agent hosted on its respective domain gateway to facilitate agent discovery.",
    "Gateway proxy agents then broadcast the capabilities of all registered agents within their domain.",
    "Upon identifying a common task, the two agents initiate collaboration, facilitated by relay gateways that manage inter-domain communication."
  ]
}